title: BRIEF-ISC Signs Agreement With The Government Of Yukon To Provide Electronic Land Title Registry System

organizations.name: electronic land title registry system reuters

text:
April 4, 2018 / 4:03 PM / in 12 minutes BRIEF-ISC Signs Agreement With The Government Of Yukon To Provide Electronic Land Title Registry System Reuters Staff 
April 4 (Reuters) - Information Services Corp: 
* ISC SIGNS AGREEMENT WITH THE GOVERNMENT OF YUKON TO PROVIDE ELECTRONIC LAND TITLE REGISTRY SYSTEM 
* TOTAL VALUE OF CONTRACT IS APPROXIMATELY $5.6 MILLION AND IS FOR A PERIOD OF 20 YEARS. Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
